FAQs

Can I generate an image and edit it for free?

Yes, when choosing Wixel’s free plan you get 10 daily AI credits to use to generate an image for free and refine it with any of Wixel’s photo editing tools.

How do I know if Wixel’s Pro plan is right for me?

Our Pro plan gives you access to all of Wixel’s high-quality templates and design elements, as well as 1,000 monthly AI credits, which enables you to generate and/or edit more images every month. If you create  images for social media, help your friends throw parties, or just enjoy designing, the Pro plan might be right for you.

What kind of editing tools does Wixel offer?

Wixel offers a number of photo editing tools including image cropping, resizing, and enhancing for color and clarity. Wixel also offers a range of photo filters, and AI tools to help you make backgrounds transparent, extend images, remove objects, and more.

How is Wixel related to Wix?

Wixel is an AI-powered design platform created by Wix. In order to use Wixel, you must create a Wix account. 

Can I apply images I create in Wixel to my Wix website?

No, you cannot directly upload designs from Wixel to your Wix website, or vice versa.

Can I use the content and images offered on Wixel for commercial purposes?

Yes, you can incorporate content and images offered on Wixel into your projects, marketing materials, and other creative endeavors for commercial purposes. However, please note the following important restrictions:

  • All usage is subject to Wix’s Terms of Use. Please review these terms to ensure compliance with any specific guidelines or limitations that may apply.

  • You may not resell or redistribute the content provided by Wix through Wixel as standalone assets.

  • You may not claim ownership or take credit for content originally provided through Wixel.
